Author: fishonthesun
Text: So maybe this will be abhorrent for you, but when I binge on super sugary stuff I find it helpful to eat something with some protein, like just some turkey or ham. The healthy food after so much unhealthy usually tells my brain "whoa we had a lot!! Time to stop!!" And then I dont get hungry or even binge-y for a while after that

Author: sickcupcake
Text: I had a bad binge last night and it caused tons of anxiety, but the past is in the past. Best we can do is learn something from it and be determined to do better. ðŸ–¤ Today is a good day.
